Sir! It's weird. Right?

26:43.680 --> 26:44.600
"Hi Dad."

26:44.680 --> 26:46.040
Dump everything on a hard
drive and send it to my cabin.

26:46.120 --> 26:48.040
"I am completely conscious of..."

26:48.120 --> 26:50.280
