26:50.600 --> 26:52.640
"and I'm really sorry for this."

26:56.720 --> 26:58.840
"Dad, remember what you said to me..."

26:58.920 --> 27:00.920
"When... I was leaving for Mumbai?"

27:05.840 --> 27:09.040
"You said... Baby, go
there and work very hard."

27:09.120 --> 27:12.640
"The harder you work,
the more successful you'll become."

27:15.000 --> 27:16.200
Try harder, my He-Man.

27:16.280 --> 27:17.800
Hot - hot Omelet.

27:17.880 --> 27:19.400
Healthy - healthy breakfast.

27:19.600 --> 27:22.080
For my boys.
- Thank you, Granny. Say thank you.

27:22.400 --> 27:25.440
Granny... I don't want an omelet.

27:25.640 --> 27:27.320
I want a peanut butter sandwich.

27:27.400 --> 27:29.240
It's healthy, good for you.

27:29.320 --> 27:30.800
Packed with proteins. Eat it.

27:30.880 --> 27:32.360
I am bored of eating omelets.

27:32.440 --> 27:33.920
Eat quietly.

27:37.000 --> 27:38.000
Oh my God.

27:38.120 --> 27:39.280
What happened?

27:40.080 --> 27:41.200
That Anita Sahani....

27:41.280 --> 27:43.120
The actress who committed suicide.

27:43.240 --> 27:45.360
Now most of the producers
and directors are saying...

27:45.440 --> 27:46.880
...that they would've
given her a role.

27:47.080 --> 27:48.800
The current generation, I tell you....

27:48.960 --> 27:50.120
A little bit of frustration
is all it takes...

27:50.200 --> 27:51.600
...to drive them to
committing suicide.

27:52.160 --> 27:54.600
They don't think about
their parents at all.

27:55.840 --> 27:56.920
When someone dies...

27:57.000 --> 27:59.360
...countless other lives
get destroyed with them.

27:59.920 --> 28:03.640
I wish this generation
wasn't so selfish.

28:03.720 --> 28:06.200
Mom... whatever happens...

28:07.000 --> 28:08.680
...there's a very good reason for it.

28:11.800 --> 28:15.040
Hey... Josh. Peanut butter sandwich.

28:17.400 --> 28:19.760
It's okay. He's a kid, let him enjoy.

28:33.440 --> 28:35.960
