guy rushed her to the hospital.

28:36.600 --> 28:38.000
She lived alone.

28:38.240 --> 28:39.360
Alone....

28:39.440 --> 28:40.320
Depressed....

28:40.560 --> 28:42.080
And she committed suicide.

28:47.840 --> 28:51.400
Why would she order pizza?
- Could be her dying wish.

28:52.360 --> 28:53.360
Eating pizza?

28:53.720 --> 28:54.920
Possible.

28:55.840 --> 28:56.800
Play the first clip.

29:03.200 --> 29:04.720
"Hi, Mom..."

29:04.920 --> 29:06.080
"Remember you said..."

29:06.200 --> 29:08.600
"...baby,
go there and work very hard."

29:08.960 --> 29:12.920
"The harder you work,
the more successful you'll become."

29:16.440 --> 29:17.760
"I came to Mumbai."

29:18.000 --> 29:19.040
Rewind.

29:20.160 --> 29:21.200
There.

29:21.280 --> 29:21.760
Now play....

29:21.840 --> 29:24.440
"The harder you work,
the more successful you'll become."

29:26.120 --> 29:29.360
"From dawn to dusk..."

29:29.440 --> 29:31.880
"...I would audition all day."

29:32.160 --> 29:34.160
"And in spite of all my efforts..."

29:37.000 --> 29:39.040
"...I was never selected for anything."
- She isn't just saying it, she's reading it out!

29:40.320 --> 29:41.400
So?

29:41.720 --> 29:43.080
Suicide notes are always written.

29:44.160 --> 29:46.920
Well, one can speak it out, too.

29:47.000 --> 29:48.360
Sure. But they aren't written
first and then read out.

29:52.680 --> 29:53.680
But....

29:53.760 --> 29:55.840
"Luck is very important here."

29:56.000 --> 29:58.000
"So it was a new factor."

29:58.360 --> 30:00.840
"Some people say
those who aren't lucky...."

30:01.120 --> 30:02.280
See....

30:07.720 --> 30:09.840
That's right, sir. She is reading it.

30:15.000 --> 30:17.040
"The future holds many
joyful experiences for you."

30:17.120 --> 30:21.000
"You'll be blessed with love,
fortune, work, good health."

30:21.080 --> 30:23.440
"There are signs of
a foreign trip as well."

30:23.640 --> 30:26.120
"Please deposit 20 rupees. Thank you."

30:29.640 --> 30:30.880
Thank you.

30:31.200 --> 30:32.760
Keep the change.

30:33.680 --> 30:34.680
Seriously?

30:34.760 --> 30:36.280
You believe in all that bullshit?

30:37.000 --> 30:38.920
It's like watching a film, Danny.

30:39.720 --> 30:40.840
It's a lie....

30:41.000 --> 30:43.840
Actually, you know it's not even real,
but it's fun.

30:45.160 --> 30:47.000
You're not telling me
what you called me here for.

30:50.840 --> 30:53.920
The Australian Centre for
Medical Science sent me an email.

30:54.200 --> 30:57.360
They are offering
a 3-year contract, and...

30:57.440 --> 30:59.000
...it's a great package.

30:59.640 --> 31:00.880
And....

31:01.920 --> 31:03.000
And?

31:05.000 --> 31:06.280
And nothing.

31:06.720 --> 31:10.000
It's just that... everything is
going the way I always wanted it to.

31:10.680 --> 31:12.360
It's unbelievable.

31:13.200 --> 31:15.000
Four months ago when
Josh suffered a major attack...

31:15.080 --> 31:16.680
...we were number 4 on the list.

31:17.200 --> 31:19.000
And what happened since then....

31:20.360 --> 31:21.840
It's impossible.

31:22.240 --> 31:24.640
He's just two donations
away from normalcy.

31:25.440 --> 31:27.920
Two donors turning
up in such a short time....

31:28.600 --> 31:30.240
It's a miracle, Danny.

31:32.680 --> 31:34.440
There are no miracles in life, Aruna.

31:36.800 --> 31:38.240
Just the once you create.

31:39.800 --> 31:41.360
Then create one for us.

31:42.760 --> 31:44.360
The mail clearly states that...

31:45.040 --> 31:47.360
...you're requested
to move... with your family.

32:06.120 --> 32:07.040
Did you have your food?

32:07.840 --> 32:08.920
Yes, I'm eating the food you packed.

32:09.000 --> 32:09.960
How did it taste?

32:10.400 --> 32:12.880
The vegetables...
are still... umm... fresh.

32:12.960 --> 32:14.400
Really delicious.

32:14.760 --> 32:16.280
Sir, should I get more
kebabs for you?

32:16.360 --> 32:17.040
Kebabs...?

32:17.120 --> 32:18.080
What kebabs?

32:18.160 --> 32:19.200
Get lost.

32:19.280 --> 32:20.160
Where are you?

32:20.240 --> 32:21.920
No... not to you.
- Where did this kebabs come from?

32:22.600 --> 32:24.920
Hey! What am I asking you?

32:25.440 --> 32:27.400
Yeah... coming, Kabir sir.

32:27.600 --> 32:28.000
Listen, hubby!

32:28.080 --> 32:29.440
I'll speak to you later.

32:38.040 --> 32:39.760
Did you pledge your organs?

32:41.640 --> 32:42.600
No, sir.

32:43.600 --> 32:45.720
The other day I just
said it for the heck of it.

32:46.040 --> 32:48.880
Honestly speaking... it's scary.

32:50.240 --> 32:52.920
What if someday I'm
admitted to a hospital...

32:53.040 --> 32:55.800
...and those guys just take
my organs out while I'm still alive!

32:59.040 --> 33:01.040
This girl donated six of her organs.

33:01.120 --> 33:03.000
How many?
