33:14.160 --> 33:16.320
...we should donate
our organs as well.

33:16.400 --> 33:18.240
When Rahul's bike was recovered...

33:18.320 --> 33:20.880
...his helmet was
tied at the back, Sir.

33:24.440 --> 33:26.600
I need a zonal list of
All organ donors in Mumbai.

33:26.800 --> 33:29.680
Hmmm?
- I want it now.

33:30.880 --> 33:33.640
Can I finish this first?
- No, come on.

33:34.000 --> 33:35.680
Clear the bill, come.
- Sir.

33:37.840 --> 33:40.720
Hey... pack everything up, fast.

33:46.440 --> 33:48.040
There are so many organ donors.

33:48.680 --> 33:50.040
How do we go through these?

33:54.200 --> 33:58.200
Here's another list of donors.
Check this, too.

34:01.360 --> 34:02.440
Sir.

34:05.120 --> 34:07.080
It's the organ mafia, sir.
100 percent.

34:07.800 --> 34:11.440
No... that's not possible.

34:12.240 --> 34:13.080
Why?

34:13.280 --> 34:15.040
It's not the organ
mafia's modus operandi.

34:15.280 --> 34:18.880
Kill the victims... and then
donate their organs.

34:19.080 --> 34:20.880
Then there can be only one culprit.

34:21.000 --> 34:22.000
Who?

34:22.120 --> 34:23.040
Coincidence.

34:24.000 --> 34:26.000
Two people were on the same organ
donors list and they both died.

34:26.080 --> 34:27.040
Coincidence.

34:28.120 --> 34:29.880
Let it go, sir... this is enough.

